original_title: Alien Chronicles: USOs and Under Water Alien Bases
overview: USOs are repeatedly seen in our oceans, lakes and seas. The military has documented several undersea encounters and are baffled by their capability to speed through the water at unfathomable speeds as if they are defying our current laws of physics, prompting the same bewilderment as with UFOs. The real concern is who are they and what do they want on planet Earth?
tagline: USOs are seen by many in our oceans and lakes defying the laws of physics and are well documented by the military, but are they extraterrestrial?
title: Alien Chronicles: USOs and Under Water Alien Bases
